reviewText: Not as advertised. I ordered this movie and trolley. There was no trolley with it. Why?

My daughter loves Mr. Rogers as much as I did. I love the sweetness and slow pace. This is a good video. I have always found the land of make believe strange and a bit over the heads of the target audience of toddlers, thus the four stars. Otherwise, I am so glad to have the chance to introduce my child to this series.
